      "span_text": "In order to move from the paired-associates problem of Experiment 1 to a real language task, we next evaluate how a simple vector accumulation model akin to Jones and Mewhort's encoding of order-only information in BEAGLE would perform on a set of semantic tasks if RPs were used in place of circular convolution."
